title: Disney Characters Do The Nae Nae Dance At Walt Disney World
text:
Disney Characters Do The Nae Nae Dance At Walt Disney World "They danced like that for a couple of hours" Ed Mazza Overnight Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 07/17/2015 
Even Disney characters are doing the Nae Nae . 
This footage from the Magic Kingdom at Walt Disney World shows Mr. Incredible and Elastigirl dancing to Silent√≥'s "Watch Me (Whip/Nae Nae)." 
"Has anyone else ever seen a Disney character dance like this?" wrote Shauna Sandiford Patterson, who captured the footage this week . "It's not your average Disney dance, but we had fun watching!" 
Along with displaying some pretty good moves, the characters from the Disney/Pixar film "The Incredibles" also had plenty of energy. 
"They danced like that for a couple of hours, too," Patterson wrote.
